  abstract={Editor’s notes: This article advocates the need for a new autonomics foundation with a focus on decision-making logic and its processes for building trustworthy autonomous systems. —Selma Saidi, TU Dortmund},
  keywords={Autonomous systems;Next generation networking;Vehicle dynamics;Robots;Ontologies;Decision making},
